data.description: Private very secluded home with recent remodel on 24.88 acres. This darling updated home is move in ready. It is nestled just inside the acreage where you are not seen from the road. The perfect getaway to provide the most privacy while also having enough open area to run some cows or horses.The interior boast warm neutral colors. Kitchen with double oven, island, and a TON of countertop space. Master bedroom with his and her walk-in closets. Each guest bedroom has it's own walk-in closet. Excellent sandy soil makes for the best gardening and great hunting right in your very own backyard. Even better still just get lost in the large mature trees that completely surround this place!
